  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nTo give gas tokens to an address we use: `vm.deal(address to, uint256 give)`\r\nBut for tokens, it works only when writing `deal(address token, address to, uint256 give)` without the `vm.` prefix.\r\nCould you make `deal` use the same syntax wether it is about gas token or ERC20 token.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
